Maria Princess of Italy 1699

Born: 26 Dec 1914, Rome, Lazio, Italy 1699

Marriage (1): Luigi Prince of Bourbon-Parma on 23 Jan 1939 in Rome, Lazio, Italy

Died: 4 Dec 2001, Mandelieu, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, France at age 86 1699

Other names for Maria were Maria Francesca Anna Romana 1708 and Princess de Savoie Maria Francesca.1709

Maria married Luigi Prince of Bourbon-Parma on 23 Jan 1939 in Rome, Lazio, Italy. (Luigi Prince of Bourbon-Parma was born on 5 Dec 1899 in Schwarzau, Bayern, Germany 1699 and died on 4 Dec 1967 in Mandelieu, Provence-Alpes-Côte d'Azur, France 1699.)
